So relaxed.

00:05:44.045 --> 00:05:46.948 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:05:47.081 --> 00:05:49.416 position:7% line:83% align:start
[RYOTA] Have you ever been down
to this level before?

00:05:49.550 --> 00:05:51.152 position:41% line:83% align:start
