00:06:20.214 --> 00:06:21.349 position:35% line:89% align:start
[shatters]

00:06:21.481 --> 00:06:23.416 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:06:23.551 --> 00:06:24.852 position:41% line:89% align:start
