must be eradicated.

00:06:44.471 --> 00:06:47.440 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RYOTA]
Right. You feeling okay?

00:06:47.575 --> 00:06:49.944 position:38% line:89% align:start
[cackles]

00:06:50.945 --> 00:06:52.580 position:38% line:89% align:start
[cracks]

00:06:53.247 --> 00:06:55.149 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RYOTA]
