00:06:58.119 --> 00:06:59.186 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:06:59.320 --> 00:07:01.689 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, those cockroslimes
are good and dead.

00:07:01.822 --> 00:07:03.224 position:19% line:89% align:start
