00:08:46.293 --> 00:08:47.995 position:19% line:89% align:start
Eve. Excellent timing.

00:08:48.129 --> 00:08:51.032 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:08:54.168 --> 00:08:56.103 position:16% line:83% align:start
