reckoning.

00:09:36.010 --> 00:09:38.179 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're doing the scary
thing again!

00:09:40.414 --> 00:09:42.483 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gun shots]

00:09:42.616 --> 00:09:45.352 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:09:49.690 --> 00:09:50.925 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:09:51.058 --> 00:09:52.760 position:38% line:89% align:start
[cackles]

00:09:57.164 --> 00:10:00.267 position:27% line:83% align:start
