00:10:03.938 --> 00:10:05.306 position:30% line:89% align:start
Give her back!

00:10:05.439 --> 00:10:08.843 position:24% line:83% align:start
Relinquish my sweet
Emily this instant!

00:10:13.848 --> 00:10:16.250 position:10% line:89% align:start
