00:10:16.383 --> 00:10:18.018 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry about that.

00:10:18.152 --> 00:10:20.121 position:16% line:83% align:start
Those things just give me
the heebie-jeebies,

00:10:20.254 --> 00:10:22.756 position:19% line:83% align:start
so I go a little crazy
when they're around.

00:10:22.890 --> 00:10:25.359 position:27% line:83% align:start
Don't you worry.
It is not your fault.

00:10:26.227 --> 00:10:30.865 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:10:39.907 --> 00:10:41.909 position:41% line:83% align:start
[ERZA]
Huh, you really didn't know?

00:10:42.042 --> 00:10:44.245 position:13% line:83% align:start
That's what always happens
when you leave dropped items

00:10:44.378 --> 00:10:46.046 position:24% line:83% align:start
