00:11:20.314 --> 00:11:23.117 position:5% line:83% align:start
I found a great new restaurant,
and I thought, if you wanted--

00:11:23.250 --> 00:11:26.588 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RYOTA]
Thanks, Erza! Bye!

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:28.355 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:11:28.489 --> 00:11:30.424 position:41% line:83% align:start
[ERZA]
What was that?

00:11:32.393 --> 00:11:36.697 position:5% line:83% align:start
[RYOTA] Once I dream up an idea.
I have to act on it right away.

00:11:37.765 --> 00:11:39.800 position:24% line:83% align:start
I got this carrot
in Telulu earlier.

00:11:39.934 --> 00:11:41.402 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hope it works.

00:11:43.170 --> 00:11:45.272 position:41% line:89% align:start
[howls]

00:11:48.242 --> 00:11:50.311 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RYOTA]
My monster bait caught you?

00:11:50.444 --> 00:11:51.412 position:38% line:89% align:start
[munches]

00:11:51.546 --> 00:11:52.846 position:10% line:89% align:start
Stop it! That carrot is not--

00:11:52.980 --> 00:11:55.983 position:19% line:83% align:start
