if I ever saw one!

00:11:56.116 --> 00:11:58.152 position:21% line:83% align:start
The skies could come
crashing down on all of us

00:11:58.285 --> 00:12:00.387 position:16% line:83% align:start
and I still wouldn't give
this precious jewel back!

00:12:00.522 --> 00:12:02.990 position:13% line:83% align:start
That's by far the longest
sentence you've ever said,

00:12:03.123 --> 00:12:04.925 position:21% line:89% align:start
and it was for that?

00:12:05.059 --> 00:12:06.661 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RYOTA]
Back to square one.

00:12:07.261 --> 00:12:09.296 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's a good thing I thought
to bring so many.

00:12:09.430 --> 00:12:11.465 position:30% line:83% align:start
I can't believe
she rabbited away

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:13.300 position:10% line:89% align:start
with nine out of ten, though.

00:12:16.638 --> 00:12:17.639 position:35% line:89% align:start
Here we go!

00:12:17.771 --> 00:12:19.206 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explodes]

